{"tid":1461354,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（轉）機場如何有令消防救護趕到支援","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:42:33.000Z","uid":261210,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7c7a1448fbdf1acfe32b20f0e97224b6681da187","tid":1461354,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/apEmK1Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FapEmK1Z.jpg&h=56ee7a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n垃圾消防署高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上載委任證是常識<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yfNSSdr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyfNSSdr.png&h=47db5185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抱歉我只有p牌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">首先我係代朋友po的，佢怕黑警會亂來清場</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實機場消防局有三間，不過大致上係處理跑道/飛機災難等，所以唔會點去車，一般年紀大d,藍絲多。幸好客運大樓一般會派赤鱲角消防局去。而機場係屬於一個（消防稱：危險地方）- 因為人多，遊客唔識逃生，一有火災就好危險等等（下刪非重點）</span><br />\n<br />\n所以機場一有火警/火警鐘誤嗚，就係屬於2號火警，已經最少派5架以上既消防車去。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有多過一個火警/求助報告，會再增派最少4架車前往</span>，簡稱（沙team)<br />\n<br />\n而點樣有多一個火警/求助報告，相信大家都會知道（機場內可能人多收唔到電話，睇直播可打電話通知消防署/個別消防局<span style=\"color: red;\">（999不是好方法）</span>）<br />\n<br />\n當然現場人士可以打爛消防喉轆隔離的火警鐘的玻璃，就會立即有消防車到。<span style=\"color: red;\">（記得打多幾個，最好唔同樓層）</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，消防除左火警外，企跳，被困屋內，手指被夾，困電梯等<span style=\"color: red;\">（每一個call都會有車去）</span><br />\n當然一定數量call後，就會唔夠車應付，請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n除左消防，仲有救護呢，一報有大量傷者都會有大量救護車到<br />\n<br />\nPs：好多中立/淺藍既消防員都轉黃，有咩事一定會儘力幫手救人的。<br />\n<br />\n但非必要請勿濫用救援服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（由於我不是駐守機場附近的消防局，所以希望有錯誤的話，其他同事幫忙指點下，幫到市民就得）"},{"pid":"c0713a48621b63658a29f6e74055aefa72cde3cf","tid":1461354,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:24:12.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"cf163cda1a7cd9aadac5a7c91f4b1bc46a6513ec","tid":1461354,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"daab558a0e127a61792f5b28d468476d6639e947","tid":1461354,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af41b1fb8fa73363137d0dd1e243dd2639cd362e","tid":1461354,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76d9887a3e18331d968bd9d2e5a8cbadcc23be0d","tid":1461354,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ec2a14ed0462ad18278a42749aa420de52d2d2e","tid":1461354,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:33:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7320dcfdb8944a495d773d4d51843968de2104b9","tid":1461354,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b390d414a03cefa016aeae917e4f5805f8fa3c59","tid":1461354,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afa32382f4af30754ba05758bd5a83d0ec57f7b6","tid":1461354,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0373121ca687ea65ece30e8c9ff20076ebee31e9","tid":1461354,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:58:45.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5697cb49ad90cbe0260a6a62cc680706cc8b1a","tid":1461354,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"4aff06c0f996338a392b588105846626e871f7d5","