0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:33:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae20c6939695fb69afb0d64c1d0732bff8f93a15","tid":1461354,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"68e0b2fbe017b87a5bd5ad5455ae843bb7a6432a","tid":1461354,"uid":157666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:42:31.000Z","msg":"今日太少人 尋日嘅1/5都無！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係香港人嘅就快d同我入黎！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日已經做左散水L<br />\n今日仲唔快d出黎補飛？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 尋日散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n          依家係機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0a10bfd5d5bfa979c58a337ff0a48e46d98120","tid":1461354,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB